Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.74,0:23:58.74,Side Bar Top,SignR,0000,0000,0000,,The shogun, Tokugawa Nobunobu, was supposed to be a bitter enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.74,0:23:58.74,Side Bar Bottom,SignL,0000,0000,0000,,What lies behind his tense expression...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.74,0:24:05.50,Side Bar Top,SignR,0000,0000,0000,,Schemes run rampant both on the surface and in space.
